title: [Cherrywood Bath]
[Private Suite, Alcove]
description: Moonlight barely passes through small opaque windows, set high into the wall.  A warm pool of water is enclosed within a half-circle of smooth stone benches.  The floor is crafted of burnished cherrywood with large black bearskin rugs strewn about.

Sunlight barely passes through small opaque windows, set high into the wall.  A warm pool of water is enclosed within a half-circle of smooth stone benches.  The floor is crafted of burnished cherrywood with large black bearskin rugs strewn about.

Nestled away from the main suite, most of the small alcove is shrouded in darkness.  Two round silver sconces cause shadows to flicker across an array of wooden doors.  A few wisps of steam creep out from beneath a thick black velvet curtain.
